To run HISAT-genotype
   ./hisat2_test_HLA_genotyping.py --aligner-list hisat2.graph --hla-list A --simulate-interval 10 --perbase-errorrate 0.3 --perbase-snprate 0.1 --num-mismatch 2 --debug paired --skip-fragment-regions 1000-1020

   ./hisat2_test_HLA_genotyping.py --aligner-list hisat2.graph --hla-list A --simulate-interval 10 --perbase-errorrate 0.3 --perbase-snprate 0.1 --num-mismatch 2 --debug paired,full --random-seed 0

   ./hisat2_test_HLA_genotyping.py --aligner-list hisat2.graph --hla-list A --simulate-interval 10 --debug paired,full --no-assembly



HISAT-genotype vs. Omixon

(1) Good match
    ./hisat2_test_HLA_genotyping.py --aligner-list hisat2.graph --hla-list A --num-mismatch 2 --reads CP/LP6005042-DNA_H03.extracted.fq.1.gz,CP/LP6005042-DNA_H03.extracted.fq.2.gz

(2) Bad match
   ./hisat2_test_HLA_genotyping.py --aligner-list hisat2.graph --hla-list A --num-mismatch 2 --reads CP/LP6005106-DNA_H02.extracted.fq.1.gz,CP/LP6005106-DNA_H02.extracted.fq.2.gz --display-alleles A*23:17,A*02:02:01:01

HISAT-genotye on Illumina Platinum Genomes
   ./hisat2_test_HLA_genotyping.py --aligner-list hisat2.graph --hla-list A --num-mismatch 2 --reads illumina/NA12878.fished_1.fq,illumina/NA12878.fished_2.fq



To extract HLA alleles and variants

   ./hisatgenotype_extract_vars.py --reference-type gene --hla-list A --inter-gap 30 --intra-gap 50

To build genotype genome

   ./hisatgenotype_build_genome.py genome.fa genotype_genome -p 3 --verbose

To genotype
   ./hisatgenotype.py --base-name genotype_6 -f -1 1.fa -2 2.fa


